      • loadServiceDiscovery

        public ServiceDiscovery loadServiceDiscovery(java.lang.String method)
        Create a ServiceDiscovery from configuration property. The given method parameter is used to find configuration property "akka.discovery.[method].class" or "[method].class". method can also be a fully class name.

        The ServiceDiscovery instance for a given method will be created once and subsequent requests for the same method will return the same instance.

        Parameters:
        method - (undocumented)
        Returns:
        (undocumented)
